Troubleshooting

FIFO Missing

Create manually:

rm -f /tmp/e320_iq.pipe
mkfifo /tmp/e320_iq.pipe

⸻

Blank GUI

Check:

* SSH stream is running
* sample rates match
* center frequency matches
* FIFO contains data

⸻

Distorted Display

Reduce gain:

--gain 30

⸻

Wrong Spectrum Span

Set matching sample rate:

--rate 1000000
--samp-rate 1000000

⸻

Safety Notes

Synthetic Mode

* No RF transmit
* No E320 required
* Safe for offline testing

Live E320 Mode

* Receive only unless you separately start TX
* No transmission occurs from this toolkit

⸻

Recommended Usage

Real RF Monitoring

./launch_e320_spectrogram.sh --freq 102700000 --rate 1000000 --gain 40

GUI Development / Testing

python3 synthetic_blocker.py > /tmp/e320_iq.pipe
python3 waterfall_sigmf.py --fifo /tmp/e320_iq.pipe --no-sigmf

Long Capture Session

./launch_e320_spectrogram.sh --chunk-seconds 30

