Summary

This toolkit gives you:

* stable E320 remote receive workflow
* modern SDR GUI on host machine
* optional SigMF capture
* synthetic RF scene generation
* no host UHD dependency

It is ideal for E320 remote monitoring, waterfall analysis, testing, and signal experimentation.
